name: Kodak*8mm*Brownie
description:
*** OFF-SERIES ***
*-_ Kodak Brownie 8mm Video Camera _-*
This is an idea I've been toying with - to showcase pieces of gear that had a long life and captured many memories. 
The goal is to pay homage to them by now capturing THEM and and manipulating the images with a combination of gear from yesterday and today.
